GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_RhetoricalDevices> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_RhetoricalDevices> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#RhetoricalDevices> ;
    narr:childCount "18"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "02e090750c8c4279ca7934f7186bf883831d71c7" ;
    narr:narration """This hub catalogs rhetorical and stylistic devices observed across the corpus, spanning extended metaphor, aphoristic compression, anaphoric structure, antithesis, and recursive self-reference. The [optometrist as iterative review model](narr:StyleObs_OptometristMetaphor) anchors the product's explanatory logic — lenses, convergence rounds, \"better through A or B?\" — sustained across multiple sections. Alongside it, [arrows/archery as productivity argument](narr:Obs_FeatherArrowsClose) closes the flocking piece (Jul 2026), with a draft flag that the EV version should pivot toward the voices question rather than land on productivity. The [road/running spatial analogy](narr:StyleObs_5) maps abstract tool behavior onto directional spatial models, while [mathematical metaphors](narr:StyleObs_5) — asymptotic approach, escape valve — frame epistemological and psychological concepts. Capitalized IS appears as a [spoken-word authority marker](narr:StyleObs_4) and as [aphoristic product principle](narr:StyleObs_CallIsMemory). Antithesis recurs as a core move — [\"not just\" inversions](narr:StyleObs_2), [\"running it, not evaluating it\"](narr:StyleObs_Antithesis), [\"It's not X, it's Y\" reframes](narr:StyleObs_VerbatimReframe). Anaphora structures both [identity claims](narr:StyleObs_Anaphora) and [imperative command sequences](narr:StyleObs_4). The [self-documenting release](narr:StyleObs_SelfDocumentingRelease) (Jul 5 2026) enacts a recursive rhetorical move — artifact describing itself as instrument. [Archetype testing](narr:StyleObs_ArchetypeTesting) (Apr 2026) and [methodology validation](narr:StyleObs_MethodologyValidation) (May 2026) mark earlier moments where principles were stress-tested against the full perspective.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_FeatherArrowsClose> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_4> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_5> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_6> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AnalogyReadableTest> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Anaphora> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Antithesis> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ArchetypeTesting> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_CallIsMemory> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_CounterIntuitivelyPowerful> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Metaphor_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_MethodologyValidation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_OptometristMetaphor> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ProductTestingItself> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_QuotedTermReframe> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SelfDocumentingRelease> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_VerbatimReframe> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "I built aswritten to feather our arrows, that our first attempt may always take us further in the direction we're headed. That our work is to adjust our heading so that all arrows find target, not spend our time moving the ones that already missed." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_5> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "testing it against every archetype in the perspective" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ArchetypeTesting> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "the cutover decision was saved as a memory through the new production pipeline, its citation offsets landing slice-exact on the first try" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SelfDocumentingRelease> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "This directly validates 2026-05-01-6-onboarding-codebase-review-topic-analysis-not-direct-ingestion — the customer's chief architect independently arrived at the same anti-pattern conclusion" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_MethodologyValidation> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "narrative operates like a velocity or acceleration vector in these particle systems" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "a readable test framework becomes the critical human review interface" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AnalogyReadableTest> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "The physics never changed. The substrate did" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_6> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "bootload a new worldview" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_6> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The arrows/archery metaphor carries a draft flag to pivot away from productivity closure toward the voices question — the metaphor's intended landing point is explicitly contested within the corpus." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_FeatherArrowsClose> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Antithesis operates at multiple registers: as process semantics (Save/Merge binary), as financial argument (revenue before raise), and as identity sharpening (running vs. evaluating) — not a single unified move but a family of distinct applications." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Antithesis> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_2> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_VerbatimReframe> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The 'counterintuitively' adverb device pre-empts objection by reframing a weakness as strength — a rhetorical posture that runs against the more declarative, non-hedging authority tone dominant elsewhere." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_CounterIntuitivelyPowerful> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Block-quoted founder voice (conversational, thinking-aloud) contrasts structurally with surrounding analytical prose — a register split that is itself a rhetorical device, not just a formatting choice." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_4> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_6> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Scare-quotes as vocabulary rejection ('infrastructure') sit in tension with the aphoristic certainty of IS-capitalization — one device signals deliberate unsettling of terms, the other asserts finality." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_QuotedTermReframe> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_CallIsMemory> ] ;
    narr:writer "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.6" .
